Create a page that uses a form to gather all the inputs (at least 20) for a Mad Lib game.  Use the php process discussed in this unit, validate and display the resulting Mad Lib. 

Use CSS and appropriate images to make your page(s) look nice.

Name your folder "madlib" and the php code with the form in it "MadLibForm.php" 

Review the Rubric to see what the requirements for the project are and how the project will be graded.

Zip all files and upload.
